03 Jun 2004 Kevin Rosenberg <kevin@rosenberg.net>
	* Version 2.11.5 released
	* examples/clsql-tutorial.lisp: Remove obsolete :nulls-ok attribute,
	Select connection-spec based on connection type. Bugs reported by
	Bill Clementson.
